data.description: Don't miss out on this exceptional 2/2 waterfront log cabin home offering captivating views of the golf course and providing deep water access to the Cedar River. This home is nestled on a spacious lot and includes a 1/1 in-law suite equipped with a full bathroom, murphy bed, and a compact kitchenette. Perfect for friends/family or income opportunities! Moreover, there is a generous workshop that features an air-conditioned office area and a convenient half bath. TONS of storage and you can utilize this space for a man cave, studio, workshop, or all of the above! Covered parking is available for your cars, RVs, and boats, along with two docks complete with a boat ramp and launch facilities. NEWER SEPTIC SYSTEM & WATER SOFTENER Home sits HIGH & DRY. Seller open to closing costs assistance. This home is in excellent condition but could also be a great candidate for a renovation loan!
